{
  "texts": [
    "RoBERTa [6] After the XLNet model outperformed the BERT model in NLP tasks, Facebook proposed the a Robustly Optimized BERT Pretraining Approach model (RoBERTa).",
    "Compared with the BERT model, the RoBERTa model does not have too many structural differences, but the methods in the pre-training phase have changed.",
    "Compared with the BERT model, the RoBERTa model has more model parameters, a larger batch size, and more training data.",
    "In addition, the RoBERTa model also has different pre-training methods.",
    "First, it deletes the next sentence prediction (NSP) task."
  ]
}